metadata.name: Across The Delta
metadata.description:
"Across The Delta" is one of our first paintings, inspired by two different musicians.
While creating ATD, we listened to a lot of Sven Van Hees & David Sanborn. Sven's album "Exotica"
houses the track which we named this painting after. We also loved the shapes and colors from the
album cover "Voyeur" by David Sanborn.

1/1 - Upon purchase, collector will receive the physical/original gallery wrapped canvas ready to hang, demanding 48x60inches of real estate on their wall!
